        "parent_id": "6a478917ca41b0118871f3973163c3bb"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "NarrativeText",
      "text": "At the heart of their dispute is JSX, a Dallas-based carrier beloved by work travelers for offering convenience like a chartered plane at near business class prices.",
